{
  "name": "The Pale Emissary",
  "type": "npc",
  "img": "icons/svg/mystery-man.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Nobody knows where the Pale Emissary came from. It appears without warning, speaks in a voice that seems to come from inside the listener's skull, and issues demands that only make sense weeks later. It does not appear to be hostile — it has never attacked anyone unprovoked — but its goals are entirely opaque and its presence causes cascading system failures in any technology within Far range. The Emissary is scouting something. What it finds will determine whether it returns alone.</p>",
